title: Persian
text: Please work more on Farsi language! For example, some of the words you use are different from the common language in Iran, and you mostly use the written form of it, so try to bring the language of the program closer to the colloquial Persian language that most people use. In general, Iranian people like Instagram very much, although many sanctions and filters in Iran have made it difficult to use Instagram, but people still use it more than all the existing programs. Thank you, there is one more thing about stores and the possibility of creating store facilities for Persian pages, please make it free and usable.
